de a second, then jump back down... And turn to see a Norse caster, yellow to me, run out of the tower.  (I'm just about right on top of the body now...) The caster, probably being warned of the assassin on top of the body, runs towards it, probably so she can unstealth and kill the assassin...  Bad idea.  /stick, pop her on the run, and now there's a nice second corpse, lying in the middle of the courtyard.  (I don't remember if I one shotted or not... I think I did)<br>Then, after a quick trip outside the keep (And a death) I make my way back in.  The blue archer must have gotten a res, because she's back.   And sitting in the exact same place I got her the first time.  I got her again, but this time at the cost of my life.. Unknown to me (Mostly because I hadn't been paying enough attention) our besieging force had just gotten jumped by the Middie reinforcements, and with our tanks no longer there to take care of the keep guards... My life didn't last very much longer.  But 3 solo kills in the middle of the keep was definately my best night ever.<br><br> <p><IMG SRC="http://www.dopplex.net/sigfile2.jpg" ALT="Caith Caidh, 35th Season Nightshade, An Claidheamh Soluis" ALIGN="middle"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uzarlaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>zarlaan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 2:04:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2042.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Kills</span><hr size=1> I have a lot that i would like to share but the two that stand out to me right now...<br><br>A Nightshade was griefing some troll thane who was yellow to me on the alb in emain.  I was with a group at the time at the portal and we had to go back and rez this thane 3 times.  